trans-unit.source: Encapsulates the XML language-related attributes of a <xref href="System.Windows.DependencyObject"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 封装 XML 与语言相关的属性的<xref href="System.Windows.DependencyObject"> </xref>。

trans-unit.source: This class implements attached property support for <xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlAttributeProperties.XmlNamespaceMaps%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlAttributeProperties.XmlnsDefinition%2A>, and <xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlAttributeProperties.XmlnsDictionary%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlAttributeProperties.XmlSpace%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 此类实现附加的属性支持<xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlAttributeProperties.XmlNamespaceMaps%2A>， <xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlAttributeProperties.XmlnsDefinition%2A>，<xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlAttributeProperties.XmlnsDictionary%2A>和<xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlAttributeProperties.XmlSpace%2A>。</xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlAttributeProperties.XmlSpace%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlAttributeProperties.XmlnsDictionary%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlAttributeProperties.XmlnsDefinition%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlAttributeProperties.XmlNamespaceMaps%2A>

trans-unit.source: These properties are generally only used by the WPF XAML parser implementation for [!INCLUDE[net_v30_short](~/add/includes/net-v30-short-md.md)] and [!INCLUDE[net_v35_short](~/add/includes/net-v35-short-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: 这些属性通常仅由使用的 WPF XAML 分析器实现[!INCLUDE[net_v30_short](~/add/includes/net-v30-short-md.md)]和[!INCLUDE[net_v35_short](~/add/includes/net-v35-short-md.md)]。

trans-unit.source: Actual user code attached property calls from XAML markup is not the primary scenario.
trans-unit.target: 从 XAML 标记的实际用户代码附加属性调用不是主方案。

trans-unit.source: The properties are implemented as attached properties primarily so that the properties can better support the property inheritance concept for dependency properties through all possible object graphs.
trans-unit.target: 主要以便属性可以更好地支持属性继承概念通过所有可能的对象关系图的依赖项属性，属性将实现为附加属性。

trans-unit.source: As such, this is really an infrastructure support class.
trans-unit.target: 在这种情况下，这实际上是一个基础结构支持类。

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Property Value Inheritance](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: 有关详细信息，请参阅[属性值继承](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)。
